# Nota: Flutter Web no lee .env en runtime.
# Configuracion recomendada: editar web/config.json (para releases) o assets/config.json (para builds).
#
# Alternativa: usar --dart-define en build (ej):
# flutter build web --release --dart-define=CONTACT_EMAIL=ventas@tuempresa.com
#
# Variables disponibles:
